title: SuperEco Market - Estados Unidos
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Fusion, Argentinian
description: Tiny organic vegetarian bar inside the old San Telmo's market. Offers vegan food options such as quinoa burguers, sandwiches, tortilla, almond milk in coffee. Sells products and food to take such as meals or fresh almond milk. This market is a very typical touristic spot with antiques and fruit shops.
